    "en": {
      "title": "Israeli missile strikes on targets in Syria",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Israel launched missile attacks on targets in Syria on Wednesday night, damaging the international airport in the northern city of Aleppo and military positions near the capital Damascus, the Syrian army announced.",
        "Local news reported that the Israeli missiles that hit the Aleppo airport came over the Mediterranean Sea.",
        "About an hour later, the military said the missiles struck military positions near Damascus and landed over the Sea of \u200b\u200bGalilee in northern Israel."
      ],
